    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Find The Flaw&quot;</strong> redefines the traditional spot-the-differences genre with a fresh, polished approach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience nice 3D isometric environments, accompanied by meticulously crafted ambient music. Engage in an unhurried search for cleverly concealed discrepancies, transforming a timeless game concept into something new and exciting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307250/extras/bc35a1b2b37d33bd197ecf5701f8dd30.avif?t=1746769716\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307250/extras_big/bc35a1b2b37d33bd197ecf5701f8dd30.avif?t=1746769716 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the meticulously designed <strong>Find The Flaw</strong> worlds, where each scene is a masterpiece of detail. Relax within the tranquil soundscapes of the game's music as you challenge your mind with intricate puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Studies suggest that playing these games can enhance your focus and boost your short-term memory, offering both entertainment and cognitive benefits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307250/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1746769716\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307250/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1746769716 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong> here. I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing everything myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
